              Here is the report from the previous analysis: {$analysis_data}

            Output strictly in JSON with the following structure:

              {
                "decisions": {
                  "TICKER1": {
                    "action": "buy/sell/short/cover/hold",
                    "quantity": integer,
                    "confidence": float between 0 and 100,
                    "reasoning": "string"
                  },
                }
              }
